{"word":"H7551 - רָקַם - râqam - raw-kam' - Embroiderer","slug":"H7551","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָקַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râqam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-kam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Embroiderer"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05E7;&#x05DD; - ra&#x0302;qam</b> - <i>raw-kam'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>variegate</i> color, that is, <i>embroider</i>; by implication to <i>fabricate: - </i>embroiderer, needlework, curiously work."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7552\">H7552</a>, <a href=\"#/H7553\">H7553</a>"}]}